    <description>Called by flow Opportunity - After Save - Experience Curriculum CW
JH - updated to also update the account EC OBS to match the EC onboarding owner
LK - 12/26/2024 - Changed the field mapping for Primary Contact on the Onboarding to map to Opportunity &quot;Primary Onboarding Contact&quot;
AC - 12/09/2025 - Added path to vreate onboardings where MRR is less than 200.</description>
    <environments>Default</environments>
    <formulas>
        <name>ECOnboardingName</name>
        <dataType>String</dataType>
        <expression>&quot;EC Onboarding -&quot; + {!get_account.Name}</expression>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
        <description>Formula to set the EC Onboarding Record Contact. New validation rule requires the Primary Onboarding Contact on the EC Opportunity record, just in case of override by manager, and the Primary Onboarding Contact is blank on the Opportunity Record, then we want to take the Contact on the Opportunity to prevent errors. LK</description>
        <name>OnboardingPrimaryContact</name>
        <dataType>String</dataType>
        <expression>IF(ISBLANK({!OpportunityRecord.Primary_Onboarding_Contact__c}), {!OpportunityRecord.Contact__c},{!OpportunityRecord.Primary_Onboarding_Contact__c} )</expression>
    </formulas>
